```

## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Cause | Fix |
|---------|-------|-----|
| Connection timeout with `requests` | TLS fingerprint blocked | Use `curl_cffi` with `impersonate="chrome131"` |
| All mirrors fail | Mirrors changed | Search for latest Sci-Hub mirrors, update `DEFAULT_SCIHUBS` |
| PDF validation fails | Got HTML error page instead | Mirror may be hijacked; try next mirror |
| PyInstaller exe crashes silently | Missing hidden imports | Add `curl_cffi.*` to `hiddenimports`, build with `console=True` first to see errors |

